{"tid":2514884,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"林祖舜：高登被污名化移民潮非首次「部分人見高登好就回流」","createTime":"2021-05-03T14:05:18.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-05T06:26:26.000Z","uid":33336,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"e0a17d9c963420c88782c42bbf6742ab6bf14f3e","tid":2514884,"uid":33336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T14:05:18.000Z","msg":"林祖舜：有啲人見高登發展好而回流<br />\n<br />\n被問及更多高登市民考慮離登移民，對吹水區失去信心是否主因？林祖舜認為「如果高登仔唔了解東方日報，甚至被誤導馬惜珍為東方日報創辦人，永遠都會有好多困難。」會盡最大努力封鎖會員。牠續指，吹水台的最大目標是令高登仔有言論自由，但每個人均有自由選擇最終在何處安居及發展。牠指，高登歷史上亦曾出現移民潮，「高登唔係未試過㗎喇」，經歷過去一年，可以理解市民會感到焦慮不安，但以往亦有部分人「見高登發展好」而回流。"},{"pid":"35db6dd1749b7152a653e1f1336be32d3f1a6014","tid":2514884,"uid":249708,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T14:06:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a35d2c575ceaff3518ee74aa774df01bab4ffad","tid":2514884,"uid":49994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T14:19:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2765675e29f6b380c5b0df9fa18b79f1b4fdbc8a","tid":2514884,"uid":33336,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"35db6dd1749b7152a653e1f1336be32d3f1a6014","tid":2514884,"uid":249708,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T14:06:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T14:25:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"065fe34466b314931d218522a72e60e0fb5d3c1b","tid":2514884,"uid":78016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T05:10:48.000Z","msg":"精神病恐懼撚 無人理<br />\n返屋企吔屎未<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a62e3b0b2a143d729e0816930a8440248e015074","tid":2514884,"uid":33336,